com.openfeint.api.resource
Class User

java.lang.Object
  com.openfeint.internal.resource.Resource
      com.openfeint.api.resource.User
Direct Known Subclasses:
CurrentUser
public class User
extends com.openfeint.internal.resource.Resource

The resource class that represents a User in OpenFeint. You use this class to get information about users, such as their profile picture and name, and make friend requests.

public void load(User.LoadCB cb)
Call this method to fill out the fields of this User object. If you've created a User with the (String resourceID) constructor and then call this method, all the remaining User fields will be filled out for the User represented by that resource ID.
